    {
      "bookmarkId": "853116_69_5282-5328",
      "chapterUid": 69,
      "range": "5282-5328",
      "markText": "他关上灯，回到了杰姆的房间里。他要在那里守护一整夜，等杰姆明天早晨醒来的时候，他还守在床边。",
      "totalCount": 35520,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=853116&chapterUid=69&rangeStart=5282&rangeEnd=5328"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "853116_67_4890-4976",
      "chapterUid": 67,
      "range": "4890-4976",
      "markText": "他嘴唇微启，露出了一个羞怯的微笑。我的眼睛里突然噙满了泪水，这位邻居的面容瞬间变得一团模糊。 “你好，怪人。”我说。",
      "totalCount": 28924,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=853116&chapterUid=67&rangeStart=4890&rangeEnd=4976"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "853116_40_8342-8373",
      "chapterUid": 40,
      "range": "8342-8373",
      "markText": "你永远也不可能真正了解一个人，除非你站在他的角度考虑问题……”",
      "totalCount": 26707,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=853116&chapterUid=40&rangeStart=8342&rangeEnd=8373"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "853116_38_3475-3615",
      "chapterUid": 38,
      "range": "3475-3615",
      "markText": "除了恐惧本身，他们没有什么可恐惧的。",
      "totalCount": 18632,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=853116&chapterUid=38&rangeStart=3475&rangeEnd=3615"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "853116_36_437-494",
      "chapterUid": 36,
      "range": "437-494",
      "markText": "我想，律师也曾经是孩子。 ——查尔斯·兰姆",
      "totalCount": 17544,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=853116&chapterUid=36&rangeStart=437&rangeEnd=494"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "853116_42_2220-2303",
      "chapterUid": 42,
      "range": "2220-2303",
      "markText": "夏天的黄昏悠长而宁静。我和莫迪小姐常常默不作声地坐在她家的前廊上，看夕阳慢慢落下，天空由金黄变成粉红，看一群群紫燕低低地掠过我们这片屋舍，消失在学校的一排排屋顶后面。",
      "totalCount": 16722,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=853116&chapterUid=42&rangeStart=2220&rangeEnd=2303"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "853116_48_6707-6746",
      "chapterUid": 48,
      "range": "6707-6746",
      "markText": "我在接受他人之前，首先要接受自己。有一种东西不能遵循从众原则，那就是人的良心。",
      "totalCount": 15691,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=853116&chapterUid=48&rangeStart=6707&rangeEnd=6746"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "853116_46_2291-2318",
      "chapterUid": 46,
      "range": "2291-2318",
      "markText": "总不能因为过去这一百年我们一败涂地，就放弃争取胜利吧。",
      "totalCount": 15228,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=853116&chapterUid=46&rangeStart=2291&rangeEnd=2318"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "853116_46_15948-16042",
      "chapterUid": 46,
      "range": "15948-16042",
      "markText": "“杰克！看在老天的分上，当一个孩子问你问题的时候，你要正儿八经地回答，不要东拉西扯，顾左右而言他。虽说孩子毕竟只是孩子，但他们会比成人更敏锐地察觉到你在回避问题，回避只会让他们糊里糊涂。”",
      "totalCount": 14229,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=853116&chapterUid=46&rangeStart=15948&rangeEnd=16042"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "853116_42_4996-5057",
      "chapterUid": 42,
      "range": "4996-5057",
      "markText": "世界上就是有那么一类人，他们——他们只顾担心来世，根本不去学习在今生如何做人。你顺着街道看过去，就知道会有什么样的后果。”",
      "totalCount": 13668,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=853116&chapterUid=42&rangeStart=4996&rangeEnd=5057"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "853116_47_1298-1339",
      "chapterUid": 47,
      "range": "1298-1339",
      "markText": "你们射多少冠蓝鸦都没关系，只要你们能打得着，但要记住一点，杀死一只知更鸟便是犯罪。",
      "totalCount": 12507,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=853116&chapterUid=47&rangeStart=1298&rangeEnd=1339"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "853116_46_17498-17549",
      "chapterUid": 46,
      "range": "17498-17549",
      "markText": "可我一直都想不明白，阿迪克斯怎么知道我在偷听？许多年过后我才恍然大悟：他其实想让我听见他说的每一个字。",
      "totalCount": 12438,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=853116&chapterUid=46&rangeStart=17498&rangeEnd=17549"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "853116_53_11339-11381",
      "chapterUid": 53,
      "range": "11339-11381",
      "markText": "阿迪克斯说过，与人交谈的礼貌做法是谈论对方感兴趣的事情，而不是大谈特谈自己的兴趣点。",
      "totalCount": 12042,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=853116&chapterUid=53&rangeStart=11339&rangeEnd=11381"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "853116_40_3056-3094",
      "chapterUid": 40,
      "range": "3056-3094",
      "markText": "早晚有一天，我会趁她不留神溜出去，跳进巴克湾把自己淹死，然后就让她后悔去吧。",
      "totalCount": 11940,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=853116&chapterUid=40&rangeStart=3056&rangeEnd=3094"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "853116_48_11110-11169",
      "chapterUid": 48,
      "range": "11110-11169",
